  "engines": ["Obrix"],
  "description": "All three processors active, all four mods routing, all three FX layers — the full modular blueprint of the reef. Saw into LP (proc1) for body, then Wavefold (proc2) for edge, then BP (proc3) as a formant slit. Coprime LFOs at 0.13 and 0.17 Hz weave a perpetual cross-rhythm that never resolves. The architecture self-organizes: every time you listen, a different brick seems loudest.",
  "tags": ["obrix", "aether", "modular", "architect", "wavefold", "formant", "perpetual-motion"],
